(3, 76, 0, 2, '<p class=\"irIKAp\">Tai ngheRedmi Buds 4 Pro l mt trong nhng chic tai nghe va hp  nghe nhc li va hp  chigame, m li c gi thnh r khi c tch hp nhiu tnh nng hp dn nh chng n ch ng ANC cc xn, pin tru v c  tr thp, ph hp vi cc nhu cu chi game.</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Redmi Buds 4 Pro l phin bn nng cp ca Redmi Buds 3 Pro nn ngoi hnh ca tai nghe ny kh cao cp. Hp ng ca tai nghe th vn nh truyn thng ca Xiaomi. Ph kin i km ch gm mt cp sc USB-C dng  sc pin cho case v cc u tips tai nghe  ngi dng thay i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Hp sc ca Redmi Buds 4 Pro c hon thin t cht liu nha v y l cht liu nha nhm m gip chng bm m hi cng nh du vn tay. Ngoi ra vic s dng cht liu nha ny cng gip chng xc dm theo thi gian. Tuy nhin phn tai nghe bn trong li c hon thin t nha bng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Hp sc ny ca Redmi Buds 4 Pro c hnh dng thon di, mt trc c n LED thng bo trng thi (trng thi kt ni v pin), mt sau l logo Redmi quen thuc, cnh di l cng sc USB-C v nt bm ghp ni Bluetooth vismartphone.</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Tai nghe Redmi Buds 4 Pro cng s dng thit k in-ear ph bin h tr cho tnh nng chng n ch ng ANC ca tai nghe. Thit k in-ear vi cc u tips s gip tai nghe c th c nh chc chn trong khoang tai ca ngi eo, t  cho cm gic thoi mi v bo ton ti a cht lng m thanh m nh sn xut mong mun.</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Do c ngoi hnh kh ging vi AirPods Pro nn phn ui tai nghe cng c thit k gn, housing to va  v c thit k nghing mt gc so vi ui tai. Phn ui tai cng l ni t pin, mic thu m v cc cm bin. Tai nghe s dng thao tc c ch chm ch khng phi bp nh AirPods Pro.</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Redmi Buds 4 Pro c driver iu khin 10mm v loa tweeter 6mm, h tr Bluetooth 5.3 v c  tr ch 59ms. Ngoi ra Redmi Buds 4 Pro cng h tr ch  m thanh 360 , mt trong nhng ch  him thy trn cc tai nghe gi thnh r.</p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"irIKAp\">Tai nghe cung cp thi lng pin ln ti 9 gi nghe nhc ch vi mt ln sc, c th m rng ln 36 gi khi dng km vi case sc. Ngoi ra Xiaomi cng tch hp kh nng chng nc IP54 cho tai nghe.</p>'),
