(26, 76, 0, 15, '<h2><strong>Loa Robot RB580  Thit k hin i, cht m mnh m</strong></h2>\r\n<p><strong>Loa Robot RB580</strong>s mang n mt tri nghim m thanh tuyt nh cho bn vi nhiu tnh nng th v. y s l mt thit b<strong>m thanh Robot</strong>rt ng  s hu nu bn l mt ngi yu thch m nhc.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Thit k ph hp vi mi khng gian, kh nng kt ni d dng</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Loa Robot RB580 en s hu thit k nh gn, thch hp  bn khng chim nhiu din tch. Cc gc ca loa c bo cong mm mi to s hin i v tinh t. Lp v loa mu en c lm nhm gip hn ch bm bi bn, vn tay. Ngoi ra, loa cn c trang b hiu ng LED RGB i mu sinh ng, thu ht mi nh nhn.</p>\r\n<p>Loa Robot RB580 en h tr kt ni Bluetooth 5.1 v ng thi s dng kt ni c dy qua cng AUX 3.5mm hoc th nh MicroSD, p ng nhu cu a dng.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Cht m sng ng mnh m, dung lng pin ln</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Loa Robot RB580 en vi thit k loa i cng sut ln, kt hp m bass siu trm cho cht lng m thanh mnh m, hiu qu tng gp 4 ln thng thng. Mng knh ng loa 52mm, cng sut ti a 10W mang n cho bn cm gic m thanh sng ng nh rp phim.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Bn cnh , loa Robot RB580 en c dung lng pin ln 1200mAh, cho bn tri nghim m thanh lin tc c th ln n 5 gi ng h. Thi gian sc pin cho thit b cng kh nhanh, ch cn cha ti 3 gi l bn  sc y li loa.</p>'),
