(28, 76, 0, 14, '<h2><strong>Bn phm c c dy DAREU EK87 - Trang b ch  n LED c o</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Bn phm c c dy<a title=\"Dareu EK87 TKL\" href=\"https://cellphones.com.vn/ban-phim-co-co-day-dareu-ek87.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>DAREU EK87</strong></a>l loi bn phm c ng o khch hng gii tr a chung. Cng tm hiu xem chi tit thm v loi bn phm ny nh!</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Thit k nh gn, b tr bn phm theo chun</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Thng hiu<a title=\"Bn phm Dareu gi r\" href=\"https://cellphones.com.vn/phu-kien/chuot-ban-phim-may-tinh/ban-phim/dareu.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>bn phm DAREU</strong></a>l bn phm chuyn dng chi game h thng Stab phm di c lm theo dng Cherry cng 2 switch ph. Bn phm DareU EK87 c thit k rt thn thin vi cc game th. Lp v bn phm c lm kh chc chn, classic. Keycap Double Shot bn b. C lp v dy, cao che kn chn switch.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Hiu nng tt v chc chn cng vi ch  led Rainbow</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Bn phm c c dy DAREU EK87 cho chng ta nhng tri nghim phm bm rt tt trong tm tin v chc chn, khng khin cho bn c cm gic b p p, kh chu.</p>\r\n<p>DareU EK87 c trang b vi c ch  led Rainbow vi  sng va phi. Bn phm c chia mu theo vng to nn mu sc a dng, sng ng hn so vi th h trc. Ngoi ra, Dareu cn cc mu bn phm HOT hin nay nh<a title=\"Dareu EK810X\" href=\"https://cellphones.com.vn/ban-phim-co-co-day-dareu-ek810x.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Dareu EK810X</strong></a>cng trang b y  n Led LRG siu phm.</p>');
