(29, 76, 0, 16, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Cui nm 2020, LG  gii thiu dng loa di ng LG XBoom Go vi din mo mi cng cht m cn bng v nhiu tnh nng thng minh dnh cho nhng ngi yu cng ngh.</p>\r\n<h1 dir=\"ltr\">Thit k n gin v thi trang</h1>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">LG XBoom Go PL5 s hu kiu dng nh gn vi kch thc ch 201 x 79 x 79mm v trng lng cha y 1kg. Chic loa di ng ny c hnh tr ngang, c bo trn  tt c cc chiu, gip sn phm v cng di ng. Phn thn loa c hon thin t nha polycarbonate vi mu en thanh lch. LG cn trang b cho chic loa ny hai vng n LED  mi bn, gip khng gian tri nghim m nhc ca bn sng ng hn.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/3ZFYnHjRepN9H2gbFpGNUkdr40sNsCEBxsCkWA2jhq8VVAZnU8M4CV5Hkjv0dsUBRpFb9ncBIIqq8whAdjWHwDKeubOuLVi1eU5jqxXagcAYA7Isnuc3a52IwJZy93gL-lmKmn4\" alt=\"n chiu t mi trng xung quanh v c th nhn thy mt trc ca XBOOM Go vi n mu xanh lam  hai u.\" width=\"698\" height=\"349\" /></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Trn chic loa ny c mt vi phm cng cho ngi dng iu hng, bao gm phm ngun, phm bluetooth, tng/gim m lng, phm dng/pht v mt phm Sound Boost.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Loa LG Xboom Go PL5 s hu kh nng khng nc v bi bn IPX5. Nh  ba tic ca bn vn khng b gin on khi chic loa ny b nc hoc gp cn ma bt cht.</p>\r\n<h1 dir=\"ltr\">Tri nghim m thanh tuyt nh</h1>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">c thit k vi cng sut 20W, LG XBOOM Go PL5 cho m lng bng n, sn sng p ng nhu cu quy si ng nht. Nh s hu cng ngh Meridian mang n m thanh cht lng ng cp. Hai loa trm c t  hai bn tri phi, kt hp cng LED, thi hn si ng vo tng bn nhc c chi. Mi nhp rung ca gii loa ny cng nh sng s mang ti nhp iu li cun cho khng gian ca bn.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/cixPfXfnotDp2Gig-7valSWVCLQWn6jbIM9ps59zAsEyhTbkhDyo7KRj7a6xYh2_zVsXO1qtf3B8jMFDxTfrZH-QQLdzNZUnCRJ5YtdYYpRJUJ2a6cIpLHM9Dgmset8N8p9aews\" alt=\"nh cn cnh loa siu trm bn tri ca LG XBOOM Go vi n mu xanh da trn trn nn en.\" width=\"953.4386291503906\" height=\"346\" /></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Vi s hp tc cng Meridian, LG mang m thanh cht lng cao