(98, 76, 0, 55, '<p>Sc D Phng WEKOME WP-333, WP-337 20000mAh,</p>\r\n<p>Pin D Phng Thit K Trong Sut Sc Nhanh QC 3.0 22.5W PD 20W Bn ang tm kim mu sc d phng sc nhanh, dung lng ln m kch thc nh gn, hy chn ngay mu sc d phng WP-333, WP-337 ca nh WEKOME. Vi thit k trong sut c o cng mn hnh led hin th dung lng pin gip bn nm r dung lng pin ca sc d phng.</p>\r\n<p>- Hng sn xut: WEKOME - Model: WP-333, WP-337</p>\r\n<p>- Dung lng pin: 10.0000mAh, 20.000mAh</p>\r\n<p>- Loi pin: Pin Li-Polymer - Cht liu: ABS + PC + Hp kim</p>\r\n<p>- Mn hnh: C mn hnh LCD hin th % pin</p>\r\n<p>- Input: Type-C 5V/3A; 9V/2A; 12V/1.5A (18W)</p>\r\n<p>- Output: TypeC: 5V/3A; 9V/2.22A; 12V/1.67A (20W Max)  USB: 5V/4.5A; 5V/3A; 9V/2A; 12V/1.5A (22.5W Max)</p>\r\n<p>- Cng sc: Type-C, USB - Mu sc: Trong sut - Kch thc sn phm: 86 x 51,6 x 35,8mm, 86 x 54.5 x 59mm</p>\r\n<p>- Trng lng sn phm: 205g, 368.5g</p>\r\n<p>-Thit k trong sut gip bn nhn r chi tit trong pin sc d phng.</p>\r\n<p>- Dung lng pin ln gip lm y dung lng pin thit b nhiu ln.</p>\r\n<p>- Tch hp mn hnh led hin th dung lng pin gip bn nm r dung lng pin ca sc d phng.</p>\r\n<p>- Trang b 2 cng sc, 1 cng Type-C, 1 cng USB h tr sc ng thi 2 thit b tin li.</p>\r\n<p>- Dng sc siu nhanh ln n 22.5W sc y 50% pin ch trong 30 pht, sc nhanh, tit kim thi gian.</p>'),
(99, 85, 0, 55, 'Pin d phng trong sut WEKOME WP-337 dung lng 20000mAh sc nhanh PD 20W'),
(100, 76, 0, 54, '<p>Powerbank t thng hiu ni ting v uy tn Baseus s rt hu ch khi bn ngc nhin v mt chic in thoi b x khi vng nh. Nh b sc khng dy MagSafe , bn s khng phi mang theo cp bn mnh (nu in thoi thng minh ca bn c chc nng sc khng dy).</p>\r\n<p>Thit k nh gn ca pin sc d phng hon ton ph hp trn mt sau in thoi thng minh ca bn vi MagSafe, v vy n s khng ln vo o camera.</p>\r\n<p>Thng s k thut:</p>\r\n<p>Thng hiu Baseus</p>\r\n<p>Loi pin: Lithium-polymer</p>\r\n<p>Kch thc: 97,4  63,8  14,7mm</p>\r\n<p>Trng lng : 140g</p>\r\n<p>Cht liu: PC + ABS</p>\r\n<p>Tng cng sut: 15W (khng dy), 20W (c dy)</p>\r\n<p>Dng ra (USB-C): 5V / 3A; 9V / 2,22A; 12V / 1.5A</p>\r\n<p>Dung lng pin: 6000mAh</p>\r\n<p>im ni bt ca sn phm: Tng thch MagSafe</p>\r\n<p>Cng sut u ra cao - sc thit b ca bn vi tc  nhanh vi cng sut 20W cho sc c dy v 15W cho sc khng dy.</p>\r\n<p>Thit k nh gn - pin d phng thm ch s nm gn trong ti ca bn! Nh kch thc ca n, bn cng c th s dng in thoi thng minh ca mnh trong khi MagSage ang sc khng dy. Powerbank s khng chng ln o camera.</p>\r\n<p>USB-C - Bao gm cp USB-C Bo mt mnh m khng c nguy c thit hi Thit hi cho thit b ny l khng th, v chc chn khng phi do sc qu mc. iu ny l do cc tnh nng mnh m ca pin polymer, cun dy cm ng bng ng nguyn cht, chip thng minh. C ti 8 chc nng khc nhau  c s dng nh: nhit  sc khng i bo v ngn mch bo v t trng bo v qu p b ngt mch qu dng bo v di in p bo v qu ti bo v qu nhit.</p>'),
