(142, 76, 0, 77, '<h3><a title=\"Tham kho in thoi Samsung Galaxy A24 6GB ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-a24\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Samsung Galaxy A24 6GB</a>tip tc s l mu in thoi tm trung c nh Samsung gii thiu n th trng Vit Nam vo thng 04/2023, my ni bt vi gi thnh r, mn hnhSuper AMOLED cng camera 50 MP chp nh sc nt.</h3>\r\n<h3>Thit k hin i vi to hnh vung vn</h3>\r\n<p>Galaxy A24 c ly cm hng thit k n t nhng mu<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi Galaxy dng A ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-samsung-galaxy-a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi Galaxy dng A</a>c ra mt trong nm 2023, my c thin hng vung vn vi to hnh phng  c phn mt lng v b khung.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/274018/samsung-galaxy-a24.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Thit k tr trung - Samsung Galaxy A24 6GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/274018/samsung-galaxy-a24.jpg\" alt=\"Thit k tr trung - Samsung Galaxy A24 6GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/274018/samsung-galaxy-a24.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Tng th chic my c cu to ch yu t nha cho c phn mt lng v khung my, iu ny gip ti u c khi lng gip cho cm gic cm nm khi s dng tr nn nh nhng hn.</p>\r\n<h3>Hin th hnh nh sng ng vi tm nn Super AMOLED</h3>\r\n<p>Chic<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi Samsung ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-samsung\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi Samsung</a>ny c s dng cng ngh mn hnh Super AMOLED, vi u im l hin th hnh nh c mu sc sng ng, ti u c in nng tiu th cng nh mang n kh nng bo v mt nh vic gim thiu lng nh sng xanh gy ra.</p>\r\n<p>My c kh nng hin th hnh nh sc nt nh  phn gii ti a c h tr ln n Full HD+ (1080 x 2340 Pixels), c b tr trn mt mn hnh c kch thc va phi khong 6.5 inch, t  mang n mt  im nh cao  c th bin mi ni dung u tr nn chn thc.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/274018/samsung-galaxy-a24-3.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mn hnh cht lng - Samsung Galaxy A24 6GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/274018/samsung-galaxy-a24-3.jpg\" alt=\"Mn hnh cht lng - Samsung Galaxy A24 6GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/274018/samsung-galaxy-a24-3.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Bn cnh nhng u im trn th my cn c h tr thm tn s qut cao 90 Hz v  sng mn hnh 1000 nits, y c th xem l hai u im ni tri m t c dng sn phm trong phn khc gi  thi im hin ti tch hp.</p>\r\n<h3>Chp nh sc nt vi camera 50 MP</h3>\r\n<p>V h thng camera ca my, Galaxy A24 c nh Samsung trang b cho b 3 ng knh vi  phn gii ti a ln n 50 MP cho cm bin chnh, km theo  s l hai camera ph c  phn gii ln lt l 5 MP v 2 MP.</p>\r\n<p>Vi b cm bin tt nh vy nn Galaxy A24 hon ton c th t tin mang n nhng bc nh c cht lng tt,  chi tit cao cng nh mu sc c ti hin li rc r nhm gip ngi dng c th s dng ngay m khng cn thm bc hu k - chnh sa.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/274018/samsung-galaxy-a24-4.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Chp nh sc nt - Samsung Galaxy A24 6GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/274018/samsung-galaxy-a24-4.jpg\" alt=\"Chp nh sc nt - Samsung Galaxy A24 6GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/274018/samsung-galaxy-a24-4.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, Galaxy A24 cn b sung thm nhiu tnh nng h tr chp nh nh AI Camera, lm p v HDR  gip cho mu sc bc hnh tr nn p mt hn, nhng vng khuyt im nh mn, tn nhang trn mt ch th cng s c x l v lm m  cho kt qu chp tr nn ng .</p>\r\n<h3>Hiu nng n nh vi chip MediaTek Helio G99</h3>\r\n<p>Galaxy A24 s c trang b con chip MediaTek Helio G99 vi mc xung nhp ti a t c l 2.2 GHz, y c nh gi l mu chip c hiu sut tt trong phn khc<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi Android ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd?g=android\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi Android</a>tm trung - gi r, va em kh nng x l tt v va ti u c nng lng tiu th  gip ko di thi gi