GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103244.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, Apple cn b sung ty chn  gip bn c th d dng iu chnh tn s qut ln 120 Hz hay xung 60 Hz ty vo nhu cu s dng, ph hp  dng trong nhng tnh hung khn cp nh ang mun tit kim pin nhm m bo thit b c th duy tr s dng di lu.</p>\r\n<h4><strong> sng 2000 nits</strong></h4>\r\n<p>So vi nhng i th khc trong phn khc th  sng 2000 nits c xem l u im vt tri m t c hng no c th snh kp, th liu n gip ch c g v c thc s hiu qu hay khng chc hn l iu c rt nhiu ngi thc mc.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103246.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\" sng mn hnh cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103246.jpg\" alt=\" sng mn hnh cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103246.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>C th l mn hnh c  sng cao  gip ch cho mnh rt nhiu trong mi nhu cu s dng hng ngy ca mnh, k t khi s dng iPhone 14 Pro Max vic xem bn  khi ang  ngoi ng lc tri nng gt cng tr nn d dng, mn hnh lc ny khng qu sp ti hay la, cc thng bo ch dn ng i cng u c th hin r rng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103249.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\" sng mn hnh cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103249.jpg\" alt=\" sng mn hnh cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103249.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Bn cnh , khi chp nh  ngoi tri nng  sng mn hnh cao cng s l mt li th, n hu ch trong lc mnh cn chnh gc chp khi mi ng li u c hin th r, ch th  c ly nt hay cha th mnh cng c th d dng quan st trc tip ngay trn mn hnh m khng cn dng tay  che chn nh sng chiu vo nh phn l