thegioididong.com/dtdd-apple-iphone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi iPhone</a>nm nay nm  thit k mn hnh, c th d dng nhn thy c l hng cng  loi b cm tai th truyn thng qua bao i iPhone bng mt hnh dng mi v cng l mt.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103229.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Thit k hnh notch mi - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103229.jpg\" alt=\"Thit k hnh notch mi - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103229.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>So vi cm tai th hnh notch nm nay  c phn tit kim din tch tng i tt, nhng khi so vi cc kiu mn hnh dng nt rui th y vn cha thc s l mt iu qu ti u cho phn mn hnh. Th nhng Apple li rt bit cch tn dng nhng nhc im  bin chng tr thnh u im mt cch ngon mc bng cch pht minh nhiu hiu ng th v.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103232.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Kch thc nh gn - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103232.jpg\" alt=\"Kch thc nh gn - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103232.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p> lm cho chng tr nn bt mt hn Apple cng  gii thiu nhiu hiu ng chuyn ng nhm lm tng s thch th cho ngi dng, iu ny c kch hot trong lc mnh n gi phn hnh notch khi ang dng cc phn mm h tr nh: Nghe nhc, ng h hn gi, ghi m,...</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103235.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Hiu ng sinh ng - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103235.jpg\" alt=\"Hiu ng sinh ng - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103235.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Hin th ni dung chn thc hn thng qua mn hnh cht lng</h3>\r\n<p>T trc n nay, tm nn OLED lun c cng ng ngi dng nh gi rt cao khi xut hin trn cc dng sn phm ca Apple, vi chic iPhone 14 Pro Max iu ny cng khng l ngoi l khi hnh nh m my mang li ht sc chn thc.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103237.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"Mn hnh cao cp - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\"Mn hnh cao cp - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103237.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Nhn vo mn hnh ta s thy c mt  trong tro v cng thch mt, ni dung hin th c chiu su, cm gic khi xem phim hay chi game cng tr nn sng ng hn.</p>\r\n<p>im vt tri nht m cc loi tm nn khc kh m t c l  chun cc v mu sc cao, mnh cng  s dng iPhone 14 Pro Max  thit k mt vi n phm nh poster hay sticker n gin v thnh qu lc in ra sau khi i chiu li vi nh trn<a title=\"Xem thm in thoi chnh hng, gi r ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi</a>th gn nh l bng nhau,  sai lch khng qu ng k gip mnh an tm hn trong vic thit k hnh nh.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103240.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\" chun xc v mu cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\" chun xc v mu cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103240.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p> phn gii mn hnh t mc 2796 x 1290 Pixels nn vic ti to hnh nh c  chi tit cao l iu ht sc d dng, hin tng nh r mn hnh l iu m mnh cha tng thy xut hin trn in thoi trong 2 tun tri nghim.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103242.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\" chi tit cc ln - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\" chi tit cc ln - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103242.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h4><strong>H tr tnh nng Always On Display</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Bn cnh s i mi v hnh notch, nm nay Apple cn trang b cho dng Pro v Pro Max thm cng ngh mn hnh Always On Display, iu ny cho php thit b khng tt mn hnh hn m vn hin th mn hnh kha vi mt  sng kh nh,   mnh c th c thng bo nhanh xem ngy gi kh thun tin.</p>\r\n<p>Xem thm:<a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/always-on-display-la-gi-co-hao-pin-khong-huong-dan-1169208\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Always On Display l g? C tn pin khng? Cch bt, tt</a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103239.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Tnh nng trn mn hnh - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103239.jpg\" alt=\"Tnh nng trn mn hnh - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103239.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Tuy nhin mn hnh lc ny kh ti nn dng ngoi tri s hi kh nhn i cht. Bn cnh , tnh nng ny cng s gim tui th pin hn so vi thng thng,  in thoi qua m khong 7 ting  ch  Always On Display th my mt khong 3 - 4% dung lng pin.</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Tn s qut 120 Hz</strong></h4>\r\n<p>iPhone 14 Pro Max c tn s qut rt cao vy nn mi thao tc hng ngy ca mnh u c phn hi nhanh chng, cm gic vut chm cng tr nn thch hn, hin tng khng hay  tr trong lc vut  c ci thin ng k so vi nhng chun mn hnh 60 Hz.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103244.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vut chm mt m - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103244.jpg\" alt=\"Vut chm mt m - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103244.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, Apple cn b sung ty chn  gip bn c th d dng iu chnh tn s qut ln 120 Hz hay xung 60 Hz ty vo nhu cu s dng, ph hp  dng trong nhng tnh hung khn cp nh ang mun tit kim pin nhm m bo thit b c th duy tr s dng di lu.</p>\r\n<h4><strong> sng 2000 nits</strong></h4>\r\n<p>So vi nhng i th khc trong phn khc th  sng 2000 nits c xem l u im vt tri m t c hng no c th snh kp, th liu n gip ch c g v c thc s hiu qu hay khng chc hn l iu c rt nhiu ngi thc mc.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103246.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\" sng mn hnh cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103246.jpg\" alt=\" sng mn hnh cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103246.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>C th l mn hnh c  sng cao  gip ch cho mnh rt nhiu trong mi nhu cu s dng hng ngy ca mnh, k t khi s dng iPhone 14 Pro Max vic xem bn  khi ang  ngoi ng lc tri nng gt cng tr nn d dng, mn hnh lc ny khng qu sp ti hay la, cc thng bo ch dn ng i cng u c th hin r rng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103249.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\" sng mn hnh cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103249.jpg\" alt=\" sng mn hnh cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103249.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Bn cnh , khi chp nh  ngoi tri nng  sng mn hnh cao cng s l mt li th, n hu ch trong lc mnh cn chnh gc chp khi mi ng li u c hin th r, ch th  c ly nt hay cha th mnh cng c th d dng quan st trc tip ngay trn mn hnh m khng cn dng tay  che chn nh sng chiu vo nh phn ln cc dng in thoi khc.</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Mt knh cng lc Ceramic Shield</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Ceramic Shield c l khng cn l thut ng qu xa l i vi phn ln ngi dng khi y c xem l loi cng ngh  tng xut hin  th h iPhone 12, chun ny ni ting vi  bn b cc cao v kh nng khng li vt xc rt tt.</p>\r\n<p>Thc t, mnh  kim tra  bn ca mt knh ny thng qua vic xy xt cc loi vt dng khc d tip xc nh: Mc kha, u dy sc, bt bi v c gng knh. Kt qu m mnh nhn c cng ht sc n tng, mn hnh gn nh khng b tn hi khi khng thy xut hin ca bt k mt vt xc no c.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103250.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mt knh khng xc - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103250.jpg\" alt=\"Mt knh khng xc - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103250.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Tuy nhin y cng l mt bi kim tra nn lc dng  xy xt l khng qu ln, v th ngi dng cng khng nn qu ch quan trc nhng tnh hung lm ri. iu ny ch gip mnh an tm hn trong vic t p in thoi ln mt phng hay  cng vi cc loi vt dng khc m khng lo b try xc.</p>\r\n<h3>Bt trn mi khonh khc thng qua camera chnh 48 MP</h3>\r\n<h4><strong>nh chp ch  thng</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Trc khi i vo phn nh gi tri nghim mnh cng im s qua thng s camera ca iPhone 14 Pro Max, thit b nm nay vn s c b tr vi cm 3 camera, trong  cm bin chnh c  phn gii 48 MP, cm bin gc rng 12 MP v cui cng l ng knh tele 12 MP. Vi thng s n tng nh vy nn my ha hn s tr thnh<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi chp nh, quay phim ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-chup-anh-quay-phim\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi chp nh, quay phim</a>hng u trong nm 2022.</p>\r\n<p>nh chp t iu kin thng cho ra kt qu lm mnh rt ng , hnh nh c ti to vi  chi tit cao, mu sc hin th rt chn thc, nh khi zoom s khng b b qu nhiu gip cho tc v phng to hay thay i khung hnh khng b thay i qu nhiu v mt cht lng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103252.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103252.jpg\" alt=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103252.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103256.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103256.jpg\" alt=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103256.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>im ng  nht v phn camera chnh l v kh nng cn bng mu cc tt, cht lng nh cho ra c gam mu trung tnh, khng xy ra hin tng m vng hay m xanh nh trn mt vi chic smartphone ca nhng i th khc trn th trng. iu ny gip vic chnh sa nh tr nn d dng hn bi mnh khng cn tinh chnh sc   a chng v mu ban u na.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103259.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103259.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h4><strong>nh chp gc siu rng</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Cn i vi ch  chp gc siu rng thng qua cm bin ph 12 MP kt qu thu c lm mnh rt ng , bc nh chp vn c  chi tit cao, mi khung cnh trc mt mnh gn nh c a ht vo trong bc nh, nhng vng m rng cng khng h b bp mo hay gim cht lng nh gip cho tng th bc hnh tr nn rt cht lng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103301.jpg\">