ult\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103308.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103308.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103310.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103310.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Cn  bc nh chp t tnh nng zoom k thut s bc nh m mnh c chp c vn kh n,  y camera ca in thoi s lm vic vi nguyn l tng t nh bn ang crop bc nh ca mnh vi khung hnh v t l nh hn, v th cht lng nh s c phn km hn so vi chp mc nh.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103312.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103312.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Nhng nh camera chnh c  phn gii ln v  chi tit thu c kh cao, cho nn khi chp bng ch  zoom k thut s th nh vn c  chi tit tt, mi vt th v khung cnh u c thu li tng i r rng.</p>\r\n<h4><strong>nh chp khung cnh nhiu mu sc</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Nm nay th Apple truyn thng kh nhiu v cc tnh nng ph cng nh loi cng ngh trn camera ca iPhone 14 Pro Max, c nhc n nhiu c l l nhng ci tn nh: Deep Fusion, Smart HDR 4 v Dolby Vision HDR.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103314.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103314.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>y c xem l nhng loi cng ngh gn nh cha c mt trn bt k mt chic in thoi Android no c, vy nn y chnh l li th vt tri m mnh nh gi rt cao trn camera ca iPhone 14 Pro Max.</p>\r\n<p>Thc t th nh chp ca in thoi cho ra c mu rt ging so vi ngoi i tht,  chi tit cc cao, nhng vng c mu sc ring bit khng thy xy ra tnh trng pha trn ln nhau, tng th bc nh lm cho mnh c cm gic nhn rt  mt.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103316.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103316.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103318.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103318.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Bi v c h tr tnh nng Deep Fusion nn my c kh nng chp tng cng l 9 tm trong qu trnh mnh chp mt bc hnh, t  my s t ng phn tch  a ra bc hnh c  chi tit cng nh cht lng tt nht  hin th. Vy nn trong khc chp mnh c xy ra tnh trng run tay nh th nh cho ra vn khng h b nhe hay mt nt.</p>\r\n<h3>Hiu nng ng kinh ngc vi chip set Apple A16 Bionic</h3>\r\n<p>Theo thng l t trc n nay ca Apple th mi ln ra mt dng in thoi mi l nh to li trnh lng thm mt con chip vi hiu nng cc khng v  th h in iPhone 14 Series s l con chip Apple A16 Bionic 6 nhn vi xung nhp ti a ln n 3.46 GHz.</p>\r\n<p>Xem thm:<a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/chip-a16-bionic-giup-iphone-14-lan-at-hieu-nang-1461587\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">nh gi chip Apple A16 Bionic chi tit v thng s v hiu nng</a></p>\r\n<p>Theo nh thng s mnh o c qua cc phn mm con chip Apple A16 Bionic t c mc im nh sau: 1887 (n nhn), 5354 (a nhn) trn Benchmark v 15508 im nh gi tng th. y qu thc l nhng con s qu khng khip, dng nh chip  vt mt gn nh ton b cc vi x l hin ang c mt trn th trng di ng trong nm 2022.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103320.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103320.jpg\" alt=\"Hiu nng mnh m - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103320.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Bi v cm trn tay mt chic my c hiu nng v i nh vy cho nn mnh cng  t tin m ngay Genshin Impact vi mc  ha cao nht  tri nghim, cht lng hnh nh cho ra phi ni l v cng p mt, mi hiu ng  ha trong game u c ti hin r nt, cc pha hnh ng nh nh nhau, tung chiu u c th hin mt m v n nh.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103323.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"nh chp t camera - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103323.jpg\" alt=\"Hiu nng mnh m - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103323.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Bn cnh , y cn l mt chic<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-ram-6gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi RAM 6 GB</a>cho nn cc thao tc v phn a nhim u c my x l d dng, dng ng thi nhiu ng dng cng khng h xy ra tnh trng khng hay load li t u mi khi mnh m li.</p>\r\n<p> phin bn ny in thoi s c tch hp sn h iu hnh iOS 16 k t khi kch hot my, c b sung hng lot cc tnh nng mi m nn mnh cm thy rt l hng khi trong qu trnh tri nghim my.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103324.jpg\">