(162, 76, 0, 87, '<h3><a title=\"Tham kho in thoi iPhone 14 Pro Max ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-14-pro-max\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">iPhone 14 Pro Max</a>mt siu phm trong gii smartphone c nh To tung ra th trng vo thng 09/2022. My trang b con chip Apple A16 Bionic v cng mnh m, i km theo  l thit k hnh mn hnh mi, ha hn mang li nhng tri nghim y mi m cho ngi dng iPhone.</h3>\r\n<h3>Thit k cao cp bn b</h3>\r\n<p>iPhone nm nay s c tha hng nt c trng t ngi anh<a title=\"Tham kho iPhone 13 Pro Max ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/iphone-13-pro-max-1tb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">iPhone 13 Pro Max</a>, vn s l khung thp khng g v mt lng knh cng lc kt hp vi to hnh vung vc hin i thng qua cch to hnh phng  cc cnh v phn mt lng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103221.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Thit k sang trng - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103221.jpg\" alt=\"Thit k sang trng - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103221.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Dng Pro nm nay c ra mt vi nhiu ty chn mu sc v trong  ni bt nht c l l phin bn Deep Purple (tm), bi v y l mt mu mi nn mang li  nhn din kh cao.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103227.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mu sc mi m - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103227.jpg\" alt=\"Mu sc mi m - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103227.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Ni bt vi thit k mn hnh mi</h3>\r\n<p>im n tng nht trn<a title=\"Xem thm iPhone chnh hng ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-apple-iphone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi iPhone</a>nm nay nm  thit k mn hnh, c th d dng nhn thy c l hng cng  loi b cm tai th truyn thng qua bao i iPhone bng mt hnh dng mi v cng l mt.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103229.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Thit k hnh notch mi - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103229.jpg\" alt=\"Thit k hnh notch mi - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103229.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>So vi cm tai th hnh notch nm nay  c phn tit kim din tch tng i tt, nhng khi so vi cc kiu mn hnh dng nt rui th y vn cha thc s l mt iu qu ti u cho phn mn hnh. Th nhng Apple li rt bit cch tn dng nhng nhc im  bin chng tr thnh u im mt cch ngon mc bng cch pht minh nhiu hiu ng th v.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103232.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Kch thc nh gn - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103232.jpg\" alt=\"Kch thc nh gn - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103232.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p> lm cho chng tr nn bt mt hn Apple cng  gii thiu nhiu hiu ng chuyn ng nhm lm tng s thch th cho ngi dng, iu ny c kch hot trong lc mnh n gi phn hnh notch khi ang dng cc phn mm h tr nh: Nghe nhc, ng h hn gi, ghi m,...</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103235.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Hiu ng sinh ng - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103235.jpg\" alt=\"Hiu ng sinh ng - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103235.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Hin th ni dung chn thc hn thng qua mn hnh cht lng</h3>\r\n<p>T trc n nay, tm nn OLED lun c cng ng ngi dng nh gi rt cao khi xut hin trn cc dng sn phm ca Apple, vi chic iPhone 14 Pro Max iu ny cng khng l ngoi l khi hnh nh m my mang li ht sc chn thc.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103237.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"Mn hnh cao cp - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\"Mn hnh cao cp - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103237.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Nhn vo mn hnh ta s thy c mt  trong tro v cng thch mt, ni dung hin th c chiu su, cm gic khi xem phim hay chi game cng tr nn sng ng hn.</p>\r\n<p>im vt tri nht m cc loi tm nn khc kh m t c l  chun cc v mu sc cao, mnh cng  s dng iPhone 14 Pro Max  thit k mt vi n phm nh poster hay sticker n gin v thnh qu lc in ra sau khi i chiu li vi nh trn<a title=\"Xem thm in thoi chnh hng, gi r ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi</a>th gn nh l bng nhau,  sai lch khng qu ng k gip mnh an tm hn trong vic thit k hnh nh.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103240.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\" chun xc v mu cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" alt=\" chun xc v mu cao - iPhone 14 Pro Max 128GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103240.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p> phn gii mn hnh t mc 2796 x 1290 Pixels nn vic ti to hnh nh c  chi tit cao l iu ht sc d dng, hin tng nh r mn hnh l iu m mnh cha tng thy xut hin trn in thoi trong 2 tun tri nghim.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/251192/iphone-14-pro-max-041222-103242.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" tit