(170, 76, 0, 91, '<h3><a title=\"Tham kho in thoi Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB</a>l chic smartphone cao cp nht ca nh Samsung, s hu cu hnh khng tng vi con chip khng cQualcomm ti u ring cho dng Galaxyv camera ln n 200 MP, xng danh l chic flagship Android c mong i nht trong nm 2023.</h3>\r\n<h3>To hnh sang trng y tinh t</h3>\r\n<p>V thit k th Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra s tip tc tha hng kiu dng sang trng n t th h trc, vn l b khung kim loi, mt lng knh cng kiu to hnh bo cong nh  cnh bn v mn hnh.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020326.jpg\"><img class=\" ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Thit k sang trng - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020326.jpg\" alt=\"Thit k sang trng - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020326.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Tuy nhin kiu bo cong ny s hi thin hng phng mt cht so vi S22 Ultra, iu ny mang n cho mnh tri nghim cm nm chc tay hn, song cng mang li cm gic d chu cho nhng lc s dng lin tc trong thi gian di.</p>\r\n<p>V mu sc, nm nay Samsung cng  cho ra cc phin bn mu nh: Tm, kem, xanh v en. Nhn chung th y l nhng mu sc cc k sang trng v lch lm, ph hp cho cc bn tr nng ng, mnh m v c bit l nhng khch hng ang l doanh nhn bi ngoi hnh ng cp v thanh lch.</p>\r\n<p>Hin trn tay mnh l bn mu xanh c trng ca Samsung, mu ny va em n s tr trung ti mi v cng va mang trn mnh mt gam mu ti  c th gi c v huyn b y m hoc.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020336.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mu sc m hoc - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020336.jpg\" alt=\"Mu sc m hoc - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020336.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p> mt lng ta c th thy Samsung trang b cho my mt lp knh cng lc c kh nng chng va p tt, c lm theo kiu nhm nh gip cho vic bm du vn tay gn nh khng thy xut hin trong qu trnh mnh tri nghim.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020340.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mt lng knh nhm - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020340.jpg\" alt=\"Mt lng knh nhm - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020340.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>V phn thit k camera th nm nay hng gn nh khng c s thay i g so vi Galaxy S22 Ultra, vn l cm camera c b tr ring l v c lm nh ln kh cao.</p>\r\n<p>Tuy nhin xung quanh cc ng knh s c thm mt lp vin cao hn so vi b mt camera, iu ny gip hn ch vic try xc b mt ng knh rt tt nn mnh cng yn tm hn trong lc dng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020347.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"V tr camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" alt=\"V tr camera - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020347.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Cn v vin xung quanh my, Galaxy S23 Ultra c bao bc bi b khung lm t nhm vi c tnh bn b, chc chn cng trng lng c ti u cc k hiu qu.</p>\r\n<p>B khung ny c lm theo kiu bng long gip my c thm mt im nhn y ni bt v thit k. Cm gic khi s vo b khung nh c ph mt lp m bng xung quanh, v th y s khng phi l v tr d xc nh mt b phn ngi ngi dng hoi nghi.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://c