" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020403.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p> thi im hin ti (04/2023), y qu thc l nhng con s rt cao v c t dng my no s hu c mc im ln nh vy. Nh vo  m Galaxy S23 Ultra t tin c th x l tt bt k tc v no vo thi im ny, hay thm ch l mang n tri nghim s dng mt m cho ti 2 - 3 nm hoc lu hn ty vo mc ch s dng.</p>\r\n<p>n vi phn tri nghim chi game th Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 dng nh  c c hi bc l gn ht sc mnh ca chip, iu ny c minh chng trong lc mnh chi qua cc ta game nh Lin Qun Mobile v Genshin Impact  mc  ha cao nht.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020407.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Tri nghim chi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020407.jpg\" alt=\"Tri nghim chi game - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020407.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p> Lin Qun Mobile, my cho php ci t mc  ha ti a thng qua cc mc  nh sau:  phn gii siu cao, cht lng hnh nh HD v cht lng chi tit cao. iu ny gp phn lm tng tri nghim chi game ca mnh khi mi ni dung u c hin th tt nht.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020412.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Bng ci dt cu hnh - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020412.jpg\" alt=\"Bng ci dt cu hnh - Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/249948/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-150423-020412.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Sau khong 2 vn game lin tc trn Galaxy S23 Ultra th mnh thy dng nh my khng gp phi bt k hin tng git lag hay chm , k c nhng lc giao tranh tng, khi m mi hiu ng hnh nh t mi tng u c hin th gn nh cng lc.</p>\r\n<p