atch-3-114.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>ng h c chng nc 5 ATM - ISO 22810:2010 cho php mnh eo khi i ma, ra tay, bi  vng nc nng,... m khng lo ngi nc xm nhp vo bn trong lm hng thit b. Tuy nhin, ngi dng cn lu  khng mang ng h thng minh vo phng xng hi, tip xc vi nc nng, ha cht,...  m bo kh nng khng nc.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lu :</strong>Chng nc trn ng h thng minh khng phi vnh cu m s b suy yu dn theo thi gian.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/304166/redmi-watch-3-484-1.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Xiaomi Redmi Watch 3 - Chng nc\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/304166/redmi-watch-3-484-1.jpg\" alt=\"Xiaomi Redmi Watch 3 - Chng nc\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/304166/redmi-watch-3-484-1.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Kt ni n nh, nghe gi ngay trn ng h</h3>\r\n<p>Ngoi cc tnh nng luyn tp v theo di sc khe th Xiaomi Redmi Watch cn c nghe gi trc tip trn ng h, v cng tin li cho ngi dng. ng h c th kt ni vi c iOS v Android sau khi ti ng dng<strong>Mi Fitness</strong>trn in thoi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Ti ng dngMi Fitness:</strong><a title=\"Ti ng dng Mi Fitness trn CH Play\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xiaomi.wearable&amp;hl=vi&amp;gl=US\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CH Play</a>|<a title=\"Ti ng dng Mi Fitness trn App Store\" href=\"https://apps.apple.com/vn/app/xiaomi-wear-lite/id1493500777\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">App Store</a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/304166/redmi-watch-3-115.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Xiaomi Redmi Watch 3 - Mi Fitness\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/304166/redmi-watch-3-115.jpg\" alt=\"Xiaomi Redmi Watch 3 - Mi Fitness\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/304166/redmi-watch-3-115.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Khi kt ni vi in thoi iOS th ng h c th nhn cuc gi quay s thng thng hoc cuc gi t ng dng (Zalo, Messenger,...). Cn in thoi Android 