(201, 76, 0, 107, '<h3><a title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh/redmi-band-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vng eo tay thng minh Xiaomi Redmi Band 2</a>mt thit b eo nh gn, bt k ai cng c th s dng. Sn phm s hu thit k hin i, a dng cc tnh nng sc khe, ch  luyn tp, kh nng kt ni n nh, thi lng pin ko di,... sn sng ng hnh cng ngi dng trong mi trng hp.</h3>\r\n<h3>V cng gn nh khi eo trn tay</h3>\r\n<p>Nhn bn ngoi, Xiaomi Redmi Band 2 khng khc g mt chic<a title=\"Xem thm nhiu sn phm ng h thng minh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ng h thng minh</a>. Sn phm c khung vin bng<strong>nha PC</strong>gip ti u khi lng, s dng<strong>knh cng lc 2.5D</strong> bo v mn hnh khi l va chm trong qu trnh s dng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-102.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2  - Thit k hin i\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-102.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2  - Thit k hin i\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-102.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Phn mt ca vng eo tay thng minh mng<strong>9.99 mm</strong>v<strong>khi lng 14.9 g</strong>, nu tnh lun phn dy th tng khi lng l<strong>26.4 g</strong>vn rt nh khi eo ln tay. Tr lc sc pin mnh gn nh khng tho sn phm ny ra khi tay, d eo lin tc nhng vn khng cm thy mi.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-103.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Mng nh\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-103.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Mng nh\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-103.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Dy ca Xiaomi Redmi Band 2 c lm t<strong>TPU</strong>tuy nhn c v hi cng nhng lc cm trn tay mnh cm thy b mt kh mn, m i nn cc bn c ln da qu nhy cm khng cn phi lo lng nh. Dy chng thm m hi tt, cc l dng  iu chnh  rng cng gip khng kh lu thng hn ch b hm b lc eo.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-106.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Dy TPU\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-106.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Dy TPU\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-106.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Xem thm vng eo tay thng minh ang bn ti thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh-xiaomi-mi-band\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vng eo tay thng minh Xiaomi</a>c trang b<strong>mn hnh 1.47 inch</strong>tuy khng ln nhng vn m bo  khng gian  mnh thao tc. S dng<strong>tm nn TFT</strong>c kh nng hin th tng i tt v c kh nng ti u nng lng. Mn hnh c  phn gii<strong>172 x 320 pixels</strong>mang n nhng ni dung r nt, mu sc sng ng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-105.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Mn hnh \" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-105.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Mn hnh \" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-105.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Do khng trang b bt k nt bm vt l no nn mi thao tc iu khin c thc hin bng cch vut chm trn mn hnh. Theo cm nhn ca mnh mn hnh kh mt, khng c  tr khi lt. Tuy nhin,  khi ng Redmi Band 2 mnh cn phi cm dy sc, kh cng knh trong ln u s dng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-104.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Mn hnh cm ng\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-104.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Mn hnh cm ng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-104.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Cp nht cc ch s sc khe nhanh chng</h3>\r\n<p>L mt chic vng eo tay thng minh, Xiaomi Redmi Band 2 chc chn khng th thiu cc tnh nng sc khe, thng qua thit b ny mnh c th:<strong>o nhp tim</strong>,<strong>theo di gic ng</strong>,<strong>o nng  oxy trong mu (SpO2)</strong>,<strong>theo di chu k kinh nguyt</strong>,<strong>o mc  stress</strong>,... thit b ny gip mnh nm bt c bn tnh trng sc khe mt cch nhanh chng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lu :</strong>y khng phi l thit b y t khng dng  chn on bnh.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-107.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Chc nng sc khe\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Chc nng sc khe\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-107.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Mnh  s dng<strong>tnh nng o SpO2</strong>rt nhiu ln trn thit b ny, kt qu cho ra nm trong khong 95 - 100% thuc mc bnh thng. Nu ch s c s bin ng bt thng th thit b cng s gi cnh bo  ngi dng iu chnh ch  sinh hot cho ph hp.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-111.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - SpO2\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - SpO2\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-111.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Chc nng o mc  stress</strong>mnh cng  tri nghim, sau khi mnh chn chc nng th cn gi yn c tay trong vi giy l  c c kt qu, kh l nhanh chng v kt qu cho ra kh chnh xc.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-112.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Mc  stress\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-112.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Mc  stress\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-112.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Tnh nng<strong>theo di chu k kinh nguyt</strong> phi n ca vng eo tay s d on thi gian rng du, thi im th thai v k kinh nguyt gip ch em chng mnh chm sc c th mt cch tt nht.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-113.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Chu k kinh nguyt\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-113.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Chu k kinh nguyt\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-113.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Rn luyn c th hiu qu hn</h3>\r\n<p>Bn cnh , Xiaomi Redmi Band 2 cn rt quan tm n vic rn luyn c th ca ngi dng khi tch hp hn 30 ch  luyn tp, a dng hnh thc t trong nh, ngoi tri hay trn my tp gm: i b, chy b, trt bng, nhy dy, khc cn cu, leo ni,... khi mnh tp luyn thit b s ghi li cc ch s c th  thun tin cho vic nh gi.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-50.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Ch  th thao\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-50.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Ch  th thao\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-50.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Mi ngy mnh u s dng luyn tp vi<strong>ch  nhy dy</strong>, s vng dy m<a title=\"Xem thm vng tay thng minh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh?g=vong-tay-thong-minh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">vng eo tay thng minh</a>ghi li c s c s chnh lch khong 10 vng so vi kt qu ghi li trn dng c nhy dy chuyn.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-109.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Ch  nhy dy\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-109.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Ch  nhy dy\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-109.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Mnh cn thc hin bi tp i b mi ti, khi so snh s bc chn ghi c trn vng eo tay v kt qu mnh t m th ch lch vi bc chn, cho thy  chnh xc kh cao trong vic thu thp d liu luyn tp.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-110.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - m s bc chn\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-110.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - m s bc chn\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-110.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Kt ni n nh, ng b nhanh chng</h3>\r\n<p>Bc u tin khi s dng vng eo tay thng minh l mnh cn phi ti ng dng Mi Fitness trn<a title=\"Tham kho thm in thoi ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi</a>v nhp y  thng tin ri kt ni vi Xiaomi Redmi Band 2. ng dng c giao din n gin, b cc gn gng d dng lm quen. Tuy nhin, khi dng trn in thoi iOS s b li phng ch trng khng c p mt.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Ti ng dngMi Fitness:</strong><a title=\"Ti ng dng Mi Fitness trn CH Play\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xiaomi.wearable&amp;hl=vi&amp;gl=US\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CH Play</a>|<a title=\"Ti ng dng Mi Fitness trn App Store\" href=\"https://apps.apple.com/vn/app/xiaomi-wear-lite/id1493500777\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">App Store</a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-114.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Mi Fitness\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-114.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Mi Fitness\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-114.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Thit b c trang b<strong>Bluetooth v5.1</strong>cho phm vi kt ni rng v  n nh cao, nhng lc mnh i hi xa in thoi th tc  nhn thng bo vn rt nhanh. Xiaomi Redmi Band 2 khng th tr li cuc gi trc tip, khi c cuc gi n mnh ch c th t chi hoc tt thng bo trn thit b.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-115.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Cuc gi\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-115.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Cuc gi\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-115.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Khi c tin nhn n vng eo tay thng minh hin th kh nhanh, thit b s dng phng ch c bn d nhn. Phn biu tng cm xc Xiaomi Redmi Band 2 s khng hin th c thay vo  l nhng  vung. Bn cnh , thit b ny cng khng th hin th logo ca cc ng dng m ch dng biu tng mc nh.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-116.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Tin nhn\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-116.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Tin nhn\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-116.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Kh nng chng nc tt, thi lng pin di</h3>\r\n<p>Vng eo tay thng minh t chun chng nc<strong>5 ATM - ISO 22810:2010</strong>nn mnh hon ton khng cn tho ra khi ra tay, tm, bi  vng nc nng,... v cng tin li trong sinh hot hng ngy. Mt iu m cc bn cn lu  l khng  thit b tip xc vi ngun nc nng, phng xng hi, ha cht,...</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lu :</strong>Kh nng chng nc trn thit b eo s suy gim theo thi gian.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-108.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Kh nng chng nc\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-108.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Kh nng chng nc\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-108.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Theo Xiaomi, vi vin<strong>pin 210 mAh</strong>chic vng eo tay ny c th hot ng<strong>khong 14 ngy</strong> ch  c bn v c tm<strong>6 ngy</strong>khi s dng nhiu tnh nng. Sau<strong>khong 2 gi</strong> sc y pin cho Xiaomi Redmi Band 2 mnh  s dng lin tc vi tt c cc tnh nng, kt qu l thit b ny ko di c gn 6 ngy trng khp vi nhng g m hng gii thiu.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lu :</strong>Mi ngi dng s c cng  s dng khc nhau nn thi gian dng thc t cng c s chnh lch.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-117.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Pin\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-117.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Pin\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-117.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>V vn tin ch phc v ngi dng</h3>\r\n<p>Vng eo tay thng minh Xiaomi Redmi Band 2 c<strong>hn 100 giao din</strong>a dng phong cch, p ng c s thch ca kh nhiu ngi dng. Ngoi ra, mnh cn c th dng nh c trong in thoi  ci lm nn giao din, khng lo b trng vi ngi khc.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-118.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Giao din\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-118.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Giao din\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-118.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, chic smartband ny cn c tch hp kh nhiu tin ch nh nh: Bo thc, ng h bm gi, tm in thoi, danh sch vic cn lm, d bo thi tit,... h tr mnh rt nhiu trong cng vic v cuc sng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-54.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Tin ch khc\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-54.jpg\" alt=\"Vng eo tay thng minh Redmi Band 2 - Tin ch khc\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/302244/redmi-band-2-54.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Vng eo tay thng minh Xiaomi Redmi Band 2 c trang b rt nhiu tnh nng sc khe, ch  luyn tp, vin pin ln, khng nc tt,... y chc chn s l mt thit b eo tay ng  bn la chn v tri nghim.</p>'),
