.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - Thit k\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054033.jpg\" alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - Thit k\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054033.jpg\" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3>Thoi mi thay i phong cch vi b su tp mt ng h a dng</h3>\r\n<p>Bn s khng cm thy nhm chn vi 88 phin bn giao din tu bin c hng trang b, trong  c 8 mt hon ton mi, 10 mt c ci tin cho php bn d dng thay i theo s thch c nhn.</p>\r\n<h3>Hiu nng mnh m n t chip Exynos W920, h iu hnh One UI Watch mt m</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Exynos W920</strong>l con chip c Samsung sn xut bng quy trnh 5 nm cho tc  x l nhanh hn 20% so vi Exynos 9110 (Samsung Galaxy Watch 3). Ngoi ra, vic s dng con chip ny cng gip tit kim pin cho cc thit b eo, em li thi lng pin tt hn cho ngi s dng.</p>\r\n<p>Samsung tng gy n tng ln vi cng ng yu thch cng ngh th gii v Vit Nam khi trnh lng h iu hnh<strong>Wear OS mi - One UI Watch</strong>, c ty bin ring cho thit b Samsung trn nn tng cng tc trc tip cng Google, gip ti u ha s ng b gia cc thit b Samsung vi nhau v ci thm c cc ng dng bn th 3, nng cao tri nghim ngi dng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054039.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - Wear OS\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054039.jpg\" alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - Wear OS\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054039.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Thoi mi tm, i ma nh ch s chng nc 5 ATM</h3>\r\n<p>Bn khng cn phi lo lng khi mang ng h i ma, i bi  vng nc nng,... nh h s<strong>chng nc 5 ATM</strong>. Lu : Khng n cc nt iu chnh khi s dng trong phng tm hi, tm nc nng,...</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054040.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - Chng nc 5 ATM\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054040.jpg\" alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - Chng nc 5 ATM\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054040.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Thi lng pin ci thin</h3>\r\n<p>ng h s hu vin pin dung lng<strong>284 mAh</strong>, cho thi gian s dng khong<strong>40 gi</strong>(cng b t hng). Tuy thi lng pin khng qu l tng, nhng Samsung  trang b cho th h Galaxy Watch mi cng ngh sc nhanh thng qua cng sc khng dy tin li vi 45% pin ch trong 30 pht, gip nhng tri nghim ca bn trn vn hn.</p>\r\n<p>Lu , thi lng thc t cn ph thuc vo cng  s dng ca ngi dng.</p>\r\n<h3>H tr nhiu tnh nng theo di sc kho</h3>\r\n<p>Sn phm eo tay ch lc ca Samsung lun c nhng tnh nng khin thit b tr nn c bit gia hng ngn chic ng h thng minh ang c mt trn th trng. Galaxy Watch5 s c trn b cc tnh nng theo di sc khe nh: in tm  ECG, o huyt p,<a title=\"Tham kho ng h thng minh h tr o nhp tim ti Thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh-do-nhip-tim\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">o nhp tim</a>,m s bc chn,<a title=\"Xem thm ng h o SpO2 ang bn ti thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh?g=do-nong-do-oxy-trong-mau-spo2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">nng  oxy trong mu</a>(SpO2),...</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, ng h cn theo di gic ng ca bn, phn tch v nh gi nng cao thng qua vic o nng  oxy trong mu, pht hin ting ngy gip ci thin cht lng ngh ngi ca bn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lu : Tnh nngo huyt pvin tm  ECG trn ng h ch h tr khi kt ni vi in thoi Samsung.</strong></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054035.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - Theo di sc kho\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054035.jpg\" alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - Theo di sc kho\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054035.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Phc v ngi dng mt cch ti u hn</h3>\r\n<p>Nh kh nng phn tch thnh phn c th vi 7 ch s sc kho: Cn nng, c xng, khi lng m, lng m c th, lng nc, ch s BMI (ch s khi c th), ch s BMR (t l trao i cht c bn) v tnh nng Xc lp mc tiu tp luyn (BIA) gip bn hiu r c th v thit lp cc mc tiu ph hp vi bn thn hn.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054037.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - BIA\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054037.jpg\" alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - BIA\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054037.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Tp luyn thm hiu qu vi tin trnh c theo di v cp nht lin tc trn ng h. Bn c th kim tra s bc chn, lng calo v thm ch l c thi quen tp luyn c ghi li y  trn Galaxy Watch5. Bn cnh , ng h cng tch hp sn hn 90 bi tp cho bn a dng tri nghim mi ngy m khng lo cm thy nhm chn.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054042.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - a dng ch  th thao\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054042.jpg\" alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch5 40mm - a dng ch  th thao\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/284932/samsung-galaxy-watch5-230822-054042.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Nhiu tin ch thng minh khc</h3>\r\n<p>Ngi dng c th tn hng cc tin ch nh: Bo thc, d bo thi tit, nhn cuc gi, bm gi m ngc,... phc v ti u cuc sng ca bn trong mi hot ng hng ngy.</p>\r\n<p>Lu : ng h khng tng thch vi cc thit b iPhone.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Product