(207, 76, 0, 110, '<h3>Trong s kin Far Out 2022, nh To Khuyt  mang n hng lot sn phm mi trong  c ng h thng minh<a title=\"Tham kho ng h Apple Watch SE 2022 kinh doanh ti Thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh/apple-watch-se-2022\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Apple Watch SE 2022</a>GPS 40mm. Mu smartwatch gi r mi nht ca Apple ny ha hn s khin cho cc iFans ng ngi khng yn khi s hu nhiu tnh nng hp dn.</h3>\r\n<h3>Kiu dng cun ht vi thit k c trng ca Apple</h3>\r\n<p>Nhn tng th,<a title=\"Tham kho dng ng h thng minh Apple Watch SE 2022 ti Thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh-apple-watch-se-2022\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ng h thng minh Apple Watch SE 2022</a>vn gi kiu thit k tng t nh th h tin nhim, tuy nhin c Apple trang b<strong>mn hnh ln hn 30%</strong>so vi phin bn Watch 3 Series, cho bn mt khng gian hin th ln hn. Tm nn<strong>OLED</strong>cng  phn gii<strong>324 x 394 pixels</strong>cng mang n nhng tri nghim v th gic tuyt vi trong bt c iu kin nh sng no.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Tham kho ng h thng minh Apple ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dong-ho-thong-minh-apple\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ng h thng minh Apple</a>c khung vin c hon thin t<strong>hp kim nhm</strong>kt hp cng dy eo silicone vi nhiu mu sc. Bn cnh , lp v xung quanh cc cm bin ca thit b  c i mi  ph hp hn vi mu sc ca ng h.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/289612/apple-watch-se-2022-2.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"ng h thng minh Apple Watch SE 2022 GPS 40mm - Thit k cun ht\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/289612/apple-watch-se-2022-2.jpg\" alt=\"ng h thng minh Apple Watch SE 2022 GPS 40mm - Thit k cun ht\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/7077/289612/apple-watch-se-2022-2.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Hiu sut nhanh hn vi b vi x l hon ton mi</h3>\r\n<p>H thng<strong>vi x l S8 SiP</strong>mi nh