-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/247517/ipad-gen-9-15.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Thi lng pin tt</h3>\r\n<p>Thit b cho dung lng pin 32.4 Wh (~ 8600 mAh) bn c th chi game, xem phim, c tin tc, kim tra email, x l cng vic ngay trn my tnh bngd dng c ngy.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/247517/ipad-gen-9-16.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Dung lng pin 32.4 Wh - iPad 9 WiFi 64GB \" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/247517/ipad-gen-9-16.jpg\" alt=\"Dung lng pin 32.4 Wh - iPad 9 WiFi 64GB \" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/247517/ipad-gen-9-16.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Ngi dng d dng sc li qua cngLightning,<a title=\"Tham kho mt s mu my tnh bng c sc nhanh ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng \" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-sac-pin-nhanh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">my tnh bng csc nhanh</a>vi dng sc ln n 20 W, gip tit kim thi gian sc v cho bn tn dng ti a cng nng ca thit b.</p>\r\n<p>My tnh bng iPad 9 WiFi 64GB sang trng v thit k, n nh v cu hnh, tin li v lot tnh nng thng minh, camera cht lng, dung lng pin n tng, la chn ph hp cho mi ngi dng.</p>'),
