(219, 76, 0, 116, '<h3>Sau khi trnh lng hng lot mu iPhone vo thng 09/2022 th Apple cng  tip tc gii thiu series iPad mi cho nm 2022. Trong <a title=\"Tham kho my tnh bng iPad 10 WiFi ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang/ipad-gen-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">iPad 10 WiFi 64GB</a>l ci tn c hng ch trng kh nhiu v vic ti u gi thnh nhm gip ngi dng c th d dng tip cn. My h tr h iu hnh iPadOS 16 cng con chip Apple A14 Bionic gip mang li hiu nng vt tri.</h3>\r\n<h3>Thit k tr trung</h3>\r\n<p>iPad 10 s c mt thit k kh quen thuc khi c hon thin vi phn vt liu ch yu l kim loi  phn mt lng, cc cnh v hai mt u c vt phng  mang li ci nhn sang trng. i km vi  l cc gc c bo trn gip cho tng th my tnh bng tr nn thanh thot v hin i hn thay v vung vc trng nh mt cun tp.</p>\r\n<p>Vi iPad th h th 10 th nh Apple mang n cho chng ta 4 phin bn vi cc mu sc nh: Bc, hng, vng v xanh. Trong  cc tone mu ca nm nay c lm m hn i cht so vi nhng th h trc , y c th xem l c im nhn dng gip ngi dng phn bit iPad 10 cc n anh ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/294103/ipad-gen-10-231022-031416.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Thit k tr trung - iPad 10 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/294103/ipad-gen-10-231022-031416.jpg\" alt=\"Thit k tr trung - iPad 10 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/294103/ipad-gen-10-231022-031416.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Mu<a title=\"Tham kho iPad ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-apple-ipad\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">iPad</a>ny ch c  mng khong 7 mm nn khi cm trn tay th my mang li cho chng ta mt ci nhn sang trng v mang tnh thi thng, iu ny l d hiu bi hin ti xu hng thit k mng nh v thanh lch ang l mc tiu m hu ht cc nh sn xut cng ngh ang hng n.</p>\r\n<p>im vt tri hn so vi phin bn<a title=\"Tham kho iPad 9 WiFi 64GB ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegio