(225, 76, 0, 119, '<h3>Sau thi gian di ch i th<a title=\"Tham kho thng tin sn phm iPad mini 6 ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang/ipad-mini-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB</a>cng  c<a title=\"Tham kho sn phm Apple kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-apple-ipad\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Apple</a>trnh lng vi thit k va quen thuc va mi l, my c nhiu ci tin trong cu hnh ln phn mm nhm gia tng li ch s dng, mang li s hi lng cao hn cho ngi dng khi la chn.</h3>\r\n<h3>Cu hnh mnh m hn, a nhim tt hn</h3>\r\n<p>iPad mini 6 c sc mnh vt tri khi so vi th h tin nhim, s dng chip x l Apple A15 Bionic 6 nhn mang n hiu nng mnh m hn v tit kim khong 15% nng lng so vi A14 Bionic.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-2.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Chip x l Apple A15 Bionic - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-2.jpg\" alt=\"Chip x l Apple A15 Bionic - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-2.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Hin ti dung lng RAM vn cha c Apple tit l, theo mt s tin n th my s c dung lng<a title=\"Tham kho my tnh bng trang b RAM 4GB ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang-ram-4gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">RAM 4 GB</a>gip kh nng a nhim tt hn, iu hnh a tc v trn iPad mini 6 s lun c trn tru, cho bn m nhiu ca s ng dng, chy cc phn mm thit k  ha hay th sc chnh sa video cht lng cao mt cch d dng.</p>\r\n<p>B nh trong 64 GB thoi mi cho nhu cu c bn, lu tr cc d liu c nhn vi danh sch nhc yu thch, hnh nh v video cc khonh khc ng nh ca bn cng ngi thn.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-3.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Dung lng b nh - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-3.jpg\" alt=\"Dung lng b nh - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-3.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Vi kh nng x l  ha nhanh hn ti 80%, iPad mini 6 gip bn m mnh vo bt c iu g bn lm. Tri nghim AR, chi cc tr chi  ha cao hay cc tc v 3D u s c x l mt m.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-4.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Kh nng x l  ha mt m - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-4.jpg\" alt=\"Kh nng x l  ha mt m - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-4.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Thit b chy h iu hnh iPadOS 15 tp trung v tin ch, tn dng ti a nht khng gian mn hnh ca iPad, giao din trc quan hn, a nhim thng minh hn v bo mt tt hn cho ngi dng c nhn.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-17.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"H iu hnh iPadOS 15 - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-17.jpg\" alt=\"H iu hnh iPadOS 15 - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-17.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Mn hnh ln hn, s dng thch hn</h3>\r\n<p>Trang b kch thc mn hnh 8.3 inch ln hn so vi cc phin bn iPad minitrc, nhng iPad mini 6 vn rt gn gng v vin mn hnh ca my  c thit k mng u bn cnh, thit b vn rt tin  mang theo gii tr, lm vic mi ni, mi lc.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-6.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Mn hnh 8.3 inch sc nt - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-6.jpg\" alt=\"Mn hnh 8.3 inch sc nt - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-6.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Tm nn IPS LCD vi cc lp tinh th lng ti to mu sc tt v to gc nhn rng hn,  sng cao h tr gam mu P3 cng cng ngh True Tone gip ngi dng d dng s dng iPad mini trong nhiu mi trng nh sng (t trong nh n ngoi tri,  nhng khu vc nh sng gt).</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-7.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Trang b tm nn IPS LCD - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-7.jpg\" alt=\"Trang b tm nn IPS LCD - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-7.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Xem thm:<a title=\"True Tone l g? C trn nhng thit b no?\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/tim-hieu-cong-nghe-man-hinh-true-tone-992705\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">True Tone l g? C trn nhng thit b no?</a></p>\r\n<p> dy my 6.3 mm cng cc cnh vin mng hn, gip my tr nn tinh t hn. Nt ngun tch hp Touch ID  cnh trn my gip truy cp thit b nhanh hn, bo mt ring t tt hn cho ngi dng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-8.gif\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Touch ID - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-8.gif\" alt=\"Touch ID - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-8.gif\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>H tr bt Apple Pencil 2c th gn t tnh v sc khng dy v cng tin li, h tr ghi ch nhanh hay tha mn am m thit k trn mn hnh iPad mini.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-9.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Thao tc nhanh chng vi Apple Pencil - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-9.jpg\" alt=\"Thao tc nhanh chng vi Apple Pencil - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-9.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>iPad mini 6 trang b kt ni WiFi 6 cho tc  giao tip kt ni cc nhanh v n nh, truyn ti d liu tc  cao khng tn nhiu thi gian ch.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-10.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"H tr kt ni Wifi 6 hin i - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-10.jpg\" alt=\"H tr kt ni Wifi 6 hin i - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-10.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Phin bn ny Apple cho ngi dng n 4 gam mu thi thng  la chn gm Xm, Hng, Tm v Trng ph hp cho nhiu c nhn vi  tui, phong cch khc nhau.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-11.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"C nhiu mu sc  la chn - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-11.jpg\" alt=\"C nhiu mu sc  la chn - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-11.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Quay phim, chp nh sc nt, video call cht lng cao</h3>\r\n<p>D khng phi l tnh nng chnh trn<a title=\"Tham kho my tnh bng chnh hng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/may-tinh-bang\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">my tnh bng</a>nhng Apple vn u t kh tt cho h thng camera ca iPad mini 6 vi camera mt trc v sau u t  phn gii 12 MP.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-13.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"B i camera n tng - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-13.jpg\" alt=\"B i camera n tng - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-13.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Camera sau gc nhn rng h tr quay phim 4K, Full HD vi cht lng tng phn tt, h tr chm ly nt, Slow Motion, Time Lapse, Panorama,...  bn thc hin nhng bc nh ngh thut v thu v nhng on video r rng, chn tht cho kho lu tr k nim ca c nhn.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-14.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Camera sau h tr nhiu tnh nng - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-14.jpg\" alt=\"Camera sau h tr nhiu tnh nng - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-14.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Camera trc quay video c th quay video Full HD gip cc cuc gi video sc nt hn khi tr chuyn vi ngi thn t xa, thc hin cc bui hc hay hp trc tuyn qua mng x hi tht tin li, thoi mi.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-12.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Camera trc 12 MP - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-12.jpg\" alt=\"Camera trc 12 MP - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-12.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Hn na camera trc cn h tr tnh nng Center Stage gip cuc gi tr ln hp dn hn khi bn c th di chuyn trong quanh khung hnh, my nh s t ng xoay  gi bn lun  trung tm khung hnh.</p>\r\n<h3>Dung lng pin tt p ng nhu cu s dng sut ngy di</h3>\r\n<p>iPad mini 6 c dung lng pin 19.3 Wh cho thi lng s dng tt, m bo p ng nhu cu s dng thit b tn sut cao sut ngy di.</p>\r\n<p>c bit,  phin bn ny, Apple ci tin cng sc sang Type-C gip iPad mini 6 kt ni d dng hn vi nhiu ph kin ngoi vi  bn thc hin cc lin kt giao tip d liu v kt ni gii tr thm linh hot, tin li.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-16.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Cng USB-C ci tin - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-16.jpg\" alt=\"Cng USB-C ci tin - iPad mini 6 WiFi 64GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/522/248091/ipad-mini-6-16.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Cc tn 