(229, 76, 0, 121, '<h3><a title=\"Tham kho mu in thoi Samsung Galaxy S23 Plus 5G 256GB ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng \" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB</a>l chic in thoi thuc dng cao cp nht ca Samsung c gii thiu vo thng 02/2023. My s hu mt vi im n tng nh camera c kh nng quay video 8K, cng vi  l con chip Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 mnh m hng u gii in thoi Android.</h3>\r\n<h3>V ngoi ng cp xng danh flagship</h3>\r\n<p>n tng u tin ca mnh khi trn tay chic Galaxy S23+ l ci nhn vung vn sang trng, tng th my c hon thin t cc loi cht liu cao cp gip mang n tri nghim cm nm m tay hn.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111218.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Thit k vung vn - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111218.jpg\" alt=\"Thit k vung vn - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111218.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Hn th, b khung nhm v mt lng knh cng lc cng mang n cho my kh nng khng xc tt hay hn ch c ri ro nt, v mi khi my c gp va chm ngoi  mun.</p>\r\n<p>V kiu hon thin th khung my c lm theo kiu nhn bng gip mang n ci nhn bt mt v sang trng hn, cng vi  l mt lng lm nhm nhm gim thiu hin tng bm du vn tay v m hi mi khi s dng, ngoi ra cc vt xc nh cng c gim thiu i vi mt lng ca chic my ny.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111223.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Khung vin nhm chc chn - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111223.jpg\" alt=\"Khung vin nhm chc chn - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111223.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Thot nhn th  phin bn Galaxy S23+ c l s khng c qu nhiu s i mi so vi th h tin nhim, tuy nhin im m ta c th d dng nhn thy v phn bit c hai mu my gia i trc v i sau l nm  phn cm camera.</p>\r\n<p>S khng cn t chung cm na, m thay vo  camera trn Galaxy S23+ u c b tr theo cch ring l, va mang n im nhn mi l xong cng em li im nhn din c trng cho dng my ny.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111355.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Cm camera ring bit - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111355.jpg\" alt=\"Cm camera ring bit - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111355.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Cn v nguyn l thit k phn mn hnh th Galaxy S23+ cng khng c qu nhiu iu khc bit, vn s l mn hnh phng vi cc vin siu mng bao bc xung quanh, cng vi  l hnh notch dng c l cha camera c lm nh  ti u din tch hin th.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111402.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Vin mn hnh mng - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111402.jpg\" alt=\"Vin mn hnh mng - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111402.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3>Bt ph mi gii hn vi chip Snapdragon 8 Gen 2</h3>\r\n<p>Vo mi dp ra mt, hng<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi Samsung ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-samsung\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi Samsung</a>s trang b nhng con chip mnh m nht c ra mt cng thi gian , v ti thi im hin ti th vi x l Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 l ci tn  xut hin trn Galaxy S23+ vi hiu nng mang li l v cng n tng.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111409.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Trang b Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111409.jpg\" alt=\"Trang b Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111409.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Theo thng s ca chip c cung cp bi hng th Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 c th hot ng vi hiu sut ti a t c l 3.36 GHz, y l con s rt ln trn nhng mu<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi Android ang kinh doanh ti Th Gii Di ng\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd?g=android\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi Android</a>khi kh t thit b t c ngng hiu nng trn.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra th mnh cng  kim chng sc mnh ca my thm mt ln na, thao tc ny c thc hin thng qua hai phn mm o hiu nng thng dng v kt qu c c nh sau: 1449 (n nhn), 4565 (a nhn) trn Benchmark v 15211 trn PCMark.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111414.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"im nh gi hiu nng - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111414.jpg\" alt=\"im nh gi hiu nng - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111414.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>V tri nghim thc t ra sao th mnh cng  dnh ra hai tun tri nghim Galaxy S23+, v nhng g mnh cm nhn c l mt  mt rt n nh m my  mang li. Mi nhu cu s dng c bn hng ngy u c x l nhanh chng v mnh cng khng h cm thy git lag hay chm .</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111418.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Hiu nng mnh m - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111418.jpg\" alt=\"Hiu nng mnh m - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111418.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Vi nhng tn  v game th Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 l ci tn thu ht c nhiu s ch  n t ngi dng, khi y c xem l mu chip mnh m bc nht dng in thoi Android hin nay.</p>\r\n<p>Thc t th mnh  dng Galaxy S23+  chi game Lin Qun Mobile trong lc tri nghim my, cu hnh c th m mnh ci t  y l gn nh ti a cho mi thng s, iu ny nhm khai thc c ti a hiu nng trn chip  th xem my mnh m ti u.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111423.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Cu hnh game - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111423.jpg\" alt=\"Cu hnh game - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111423.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Kt qu th Galaxy S23+ vn tha sc x l c ta game ny, my gn nh khng gp phi kh khn no trong lc mnh s dng, mi th u c din ra mt m vi tc  khung hnh duy tr n nh  mc loanh toanh 60 FPS.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111427.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Cu hnh game - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111427.jpg\" alt=\"Cu hnh game - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111427.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Chuyn n ta game kh hn l Genshin Impact, y c nh gi l tr chi i hi hiu nng ca thit b phi tht mnh m, v l ci tn xng tm  test th hiu nng ca Galaxy S23+.</p>\r\n<p>Cu hnh  ta game ny vn tip tc l mc ci t cao nht m my c th t c, bi v mnh mun tri nghim c hnh nh vi cht lng nht m ta game ny hin th ra sao, v n c thc s lm kh c Galaxy S23+.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111435.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Cu hnh game - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111435.jpg\" alt=\"Cu hnh game - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111435.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111440.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" title=\"Cu hnh game - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111440.jpg\" alt=\"Cu hnh game - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111440.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Mnh kh bt ng khi tri nghim thc t qua ta game ny  mc cu hnh cao m my vn c th x l tt, mc FPS lun c dao ng trong tm t 35 - 45 v t khi xy ra hin tng drop qu su, n gip cho tnh trng git hay  my t khi xy ra.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111445.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"Cu hnh game - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" alt=\"Cu hnh game - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111445.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Nhit  do chip ta ra lun l cu hi c ngi dng quan tm trn nhng mu chip i cao, v nu nh  Gen 1 c xut hin tnh trng qu nhit trong lc chi game  mt vi dng my n t cc hng khc. Th i vi Gen 2, y l mt bc tin ln t nh Samsung khi hp tc vi Qualcomm  sn xut ra mu chip chuyn dng c quyn cho Galaxy.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111450.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"Kh nng tn nhit - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" alt=\"Kh nng tn nhit - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111450.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Nh iu  m Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 tng thch vi in thoi tt hn, hot ng vi hiu sut cao v cng ci thin c tnh trng qu nhit. Vi khong 2 gi chi game lin tc  mi trng nhit  phng, mnh gn nh khng cm thy c s nng ln qu ng k c trn thn my, ch hi m nh v vn c th thoi mi  tip tc s dng.</p>\r\n<p>Bn cnhmt con chip mang hiu nng mnh mth y cn l<a title=\"Tham kho in thoi c RAM 8 GB kinh doanh ti Thegioididong.com\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd-ram-8gb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in thoi RAM 8 GB</a>, iu ny khng ch gip mnh s dng cc tc v a nhim mt m hn m cn ci thin c hin tng ti li ng dng t u.</p>\r\n<h3>To nn kit tc ch qua mt c chm</h3>\r\n<p>Vi cc mu in thoi thuc b sn phm Samsung Galaxy dng S trong mt vi nm gn y, hng u mnh danh cc thit b ny l s hu cm camera chun danh mt thn bng m v vi Galaxy S23+ cng khng nm trong ngoi l.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111500.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"Camera cht lng cao - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" alt=\"Camera cht lng cao - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111500.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>V thng s cho phn my nh th Galaxy S23+ c trang b cm gm 3 ng knh, u tin s l camera chnh c  phn gii ti 50 MP v c h tr gc rng, sau  s l hai cm bin ph c  phn gii ln lt l 10 MP v 12 MP  b sung thm tnh nng chp nh zoom v gc siu rng.</p>\r\n<p>i vi ch  chp nh mc nh th bc hnh m my thu c c  chi tit tt, cc vng sng ti c ti hin li v tch bch r rng. Mu sc ca nh cho ra s c mt  rc r p mt hn so vi thc t, iu ny gip bc nh chp c c th s dng ngy m khng cn hu k chnh mu qu nhiu.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111508.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"nh chp t in thoi - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" alt=\"nh chp t in thoi - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111508.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>n vi ch  chp nh zoom, Galaxy S23+ c h tr kh nng zoom quang hc nn khi s dng  mc iu chnh khong 3X th cht lng nh gn nh khng c qu nhiu s khc bit i vi ch  mc nh.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111515.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"nh chp t in thoi - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" alt=\"nh chp t in thoi - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111515.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Cc vng trong bc nh u c ti hin r, mu sc ti mi cng  tiu c ln gip cho bc nh trng ngh thut v p mt hn rt nhiu. Tuy nhin nu xt v  chi tit khi zoom nh th ch  ny s khng bng so vi ch  mc nh.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111521.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"nh chp t in thoi - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" alt=\"nh chp t in thoi - Samsung Galaxy S23+ 5G 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111521.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Vi tnh nng gc siu rng,  phn ny my s cho php ta chp c cc bc nh c tm bao qut ln hn, gip thu c nhiu ni dung v khung cnh hn trong mt ln chp, ph hp  lu li cc bc nh nhm ng ngi hay thu li v p ca cc khung cnh rng ln.</p>\r\n<p>Nh bc nh bn di, nhng vng m rng  xung quanh ra nh s khng b bp mo hay gim cht lng nh, v th mi bc nh chp c t tnh nng ny vn s mang n kt qu tt dnh cho bn.</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/42/290829/samsung-galaxy-s23-plus-080423-111529.jpg\"><img class=\"lazyload\" title=\"nh chp t in thoi - Samsung Gal